{"tid":635992,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"麥當勞 手機落Order QR Code網 by hkfood.review","createTime":"2018-04-20T12:54:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-19T10:56:02.000Z","uid":164435,"like":13,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"62caaad6e7c9ce0d75be54b03d98d3aff232e917","tid":635992,"uid":164435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T12:54:34.000Z","msg":"見到有巴打都整咗個QR Code網<br />\n我都整咗一個<br />\n<a href=\"https://qr.hkfood.review/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fqr.hkfood.review%2F&d=u4vMZptKPzrsiD3c04Gvk9r9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=226a954e\" target=\"_blank\">https://qr.hkfood.review/</a><br />\n<br />\n暫時有42間麥當勞嘅QR Code<br />\n<br />\n如果你哋有去麥當勞嘅話<br />\n可以將QR Code或者收據上面嘅地址影上嚟<br />\n我哋需要收集全港麥當勞嘅QR Code或者分店編號都可以<br />\n<br />\n呢啲就係肯定咗喺麥當勞網站搵唔到佢哋嘅分店編號<br />\n一定要落分店影QR Code<br />\n<a href=\"https://qr.hkfood.review/2018/04/without-qr-code.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fqr.hkfood.review%2F2018%2F04%2Fwithout-qr-code.html&d=u4vMZptKPzrsiD3c04Gvk9r9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=e3bbb9f1\" target=\"_blank\">https://qr.hkfood.review/2018/04/without-qr-code.html</a><br />\n<br />\n另外呢個網遲啲應該會擺廣告嘅"},{"pid":"3bbedeac74dd9396e3392122b6c05e8903721f7d","tid":635992,"uid":164435,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T12:54:52.000Z","msg":"所有喺網站上面嘅QR Code都係重新製作嘅<br />\n所以一定要揀啱分店<br />\n如果我哋個Code整錯咗的話，個App就唔會比你落單<br />\n會顯示個Code嘅分店同你揀嘅分店唔同<br />\n<br />\n呢排比較忙 但係如果各位有影低QR Code Up上嚟我就會盡量抽時間Update㗎喇"},{"pid":"21d5000b1e0b57d09bdeb895633a8f8701df5268","tid":635992,"uid":130033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T10:56:02.000Z","msg":"多謝分享"}]}